CatDescriptText: Guests include: unknown woman holding dog "Le Jazz Petit", and Wilda Harper Sellers in front; Jimmy Harper, Ann, Alex, unknown man, Frances Harper Whitehead, Alfaretta Calloway, George Bowdry, Doris Harper Bowdry, Mrs. Austin, and unknown woman in second row; Lewis Ellis, Jay Harper, unknown, Nate Harper, and Della Pennywell in third row; and behind the fence: Charles "Chuck" Harper, Ernie Harper, Alice Harper, Matt Sellers, Walt Harper wearing shirt with light colored trim, Mark Pennywell, and unknown boy.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Harper family reunion, including brothers, sisters, and family friends, gathered around picnic table with patio umbrella, another version
